title: Resort Style Luxury Amenites! Midrise!
posting_body: Mid-rise Living Near The Galleria * Spectacular City Views *
A fantastic place to call home!

Our mid-rise apartment homes offer unique interiors including hardwood and ceramic tile flooring, granite in the kitchen and bath, track lighting, built-in bookcases and computer desk, electric stone fireplace, crown molding, storage and full-size washer/dryer connections.
Spectacular amenities include resort-style pool with misted pavilion, bar seating and stainless steel BBQs, fitness center with HDTV.

Available next door: racquetball, indoor basketball, lighted tennis, putting green sand and water volleyball, jogging trail and eight acres of parkland , onsite dog park, arcade game room and playground.
